# ğŸ“š ClassTeacherPortal â€” Android App

> A complete Android application for school teachers to manage attendance, homework, timetable, and student data. Built using Java and XML with backend APIs for data persistence.  

## ğŸš€ Project Overview

ClassTeacherPortal is built to digitize and streamline the day-to-day classroom management tasks for teachers. Instead of paper-based records, this app allows marking attendance, uploading homework, managing timetables, and fetching class/student details via API â€” all from a mobile device.

**Core Purpose:**  
- Simplify attendance tracking (daily and monthly views)  
- Enable teachers to assign homework with attachments  
- Provide class & section management, student lists  
- Maintain teacher login and profile via secure API-based authentication  

---

## ğŸ“¦ Features

- ğŸ” **Login Authentication** â€” Secure teacher login using staff ID  
- ğŸ“… **Attendance Module**  
  - Mark daily attendance for students  
  - Prevent duplicate attendance submission for the same date  
  - View monthly attendance in a calendar-style grid (per student per date)  
- ğŸ“ **Homework Module**  
  - Add homework with subject, date and optional file (PDF / Image)  
  - View list of homework entries and download attachments  
- ğŸ‘¨â€ğŸ“ **Student & Class Management**  
  - Fetch class & section based on logged-in teacher  
  - Display student list for selected class/section  
- ğŸ—“ï¸ **Timetable and Other Utilities** *(if implemented)*  
- ğŸ“± **Clean UI using Android XML layouts**  
- ğŸŒ **Backend Communication with REST APIs** using Volley library  
- ğŸ” **Session Management** via SharedPreferences  

